# Swinerton Takt Planning Platform

Complete Takt planning application with Phase 1-4 UI and Phase 2B risk/buffer logic.

## Quick Start

```bash
pip install -r requirements.txt
streamlit run swinerton_takt_platform.py
```

## Features

- **Phase 1**: Field reference cards (ADM 8-constraint model)
- **Phase 2**: Takt analysis & schedule optimization
- **Phase 2B**: Risk management & strategic buffer placement
- **Phase 3/4**: UI ready (coming soon)

## Deploy to Cloud

Deployed on Render (free tier). See DEPLOY_TO_CLOUD.md for instructions.

